               <msContents>
                  <summary>Anaphora of Our Lady, ቅዳሴ" ማርያም", Image of the Trinity, መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡, Excerpt from Image of the Passion Week, መልክአ፡ ሕማማት፡ (ሰላምታ፡ ዘሰሙነ፡ ሕማማት፡)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="48v" facs="005"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2037Naakkw"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>arranged by a later hand for the days of the week</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="51r" to="71r" facs="055"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2736RepCh20"/><incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለህላዌክሙ፡ ዘይመውእ፡ ህላውያተ፡
                  ለረኪበ፡ ስሙ፡ ኅቡዕ፡ ሶበ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ተምኒተ፡
